    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks for that. so if he gets sick or something, the person he picks basically takes over his accounts and stuff? i just want to make sure his assets stay safe and everything is protected. is there anything else i should look out for to make sure someone doesn't just mess things up or take advantage of him?",
